    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a \"period\" of feeling this way. it's like the pilot light went out. there's no \"me\" left to actually experience the \"being\" you're talking about. it's just... empty. i'm just a physical object at this point. i feel like i'm just taking up space that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
